Class AbstractRetrieverTask

java.lang.Object

      com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.AbstractTeamBuildTask

Direct Known Subclasses:
com.ibm.team.build.internal.ant.AbstractContentRetrieverTask, BuildResultRetrieverTask, DeleteBuildResultTask
public abstract class AbstractRetrieverTask
extends AbstractTeamBuildTask

Base ant task for retrieving data from an existing build result in the team repository. Ant tasks that need to retrieve information from an existing build result should subclass this class.

Required attributes are:

Note: Only one of the two below is required in any given invocation of the task. They are mutually exclusively.

  • buildResultUUID - The uuid of the build result to retrieve.
  • buildDefinitionId - The build definition id of which to get the last completed non-personal build result.

See AbstractTeamBuildTask for additional required and option attributes.

Since:
0.8.5
